node.headline: How to buy crypto with MetaMask

childMarkdownRemark.html:
Onboard to crypto with MetaMask. Just click on the Buy button on the MetaMask browser extension or mobile app to get started. You can also connect your wallet to MetaMask Portfolio to get started.

MetaMask shows you competitive quotes based on your region, your preferred payment method, the token you want to buy, and the providers that are available to you.

With a funded MetaMask wallet, youre ready to explore web3 on your own terms.

Onboarding to crypto has never been easier. Visit MetaMask Portfolio and click the Buy button to get started. You can buy crypto with PayPal, credit card, or with many other payment options.

MetaMask shows you competitive quotes based on your region, your preferred payment method, the token you want to buy, and the providers that are available to you.

With MetaMask Portfolio, you can unlock the full potential of DeFi and explore all that web3 has to offer.

node.headline: A convenient way to buy cryptocurrency

childMarkdownRemark.html: Our providers generally support credit and debit cards such as Visa and Mastercard.
You can buy crypto with Apple Pay, Google Pay, and PayPal (where available).
You can use ACH transfer in the USA and SEPA in Europe.
Our providers also support a wide selection of alternative local payment methods.

childMarkdownRemark.html:
Each payment method has a different fee structure based on the region. Generally speaking, credit or debit transactions are more expensive with lower limits while bank transfers have fewer fees and higher purchase limits.

When using these methods, you can expect to pay a processing fee, a MetaMask fee, and a market rate for gas.

Some users end up paying gas fees twice: once when they buy on a centralized exchange or elsewhere, and then again when depositing into MetaMask.

Buying cryptocurrency on MetaMask eliminates this double cost and has the added benefit of making your funds available immediately without a holding period.

node.headline: Own your crypto in a private and secure way

childMarkdownRemark.html: MetaMask does not storenor has access toany personal information you provide when buying crypto, such as payment details, personal data, or email addresses.

Unlike a centralized exchange, neither MetaMask nor our partners have access to the cryptocurrencies after you purchase or transfer them, meaning you can access your assets immediately without a holding period.
MetaMask ensures that all of our providers comply with applicable regulations and that they are legitimate, responsible parties.

childMarkdownRemark.html: You can buy stablecoins and native tokens directly within MetaMask globally across a wide variety of networks: Ethereum, Polygon, Linea, Binance Smart Chain, Avalanche, Fantom, Celo, Optimism, and Arbitrum among others.
Buy crypto how you want, when you want
You can easily buy Ethereum or other cryptocurrencies through our vetted partners.
You can buy crypto with your preferred payment method through our simple partner integrations.
You can expect favorable quotes from many of our providers with low fees and minimal shifts in exchange rates, regardless of how much crypto you buy.
